Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:39.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}现在, 戴尔, 仔细听好了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Dale, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:42.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}该你走了.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:45.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}请你用心去走好每一步,\N你会的吧?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.95,0:01:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please put your heart into it,\Nwill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:48.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}我已经注意到你思想里\N存在了某些犹豫不决的特性,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l've noticed a certain tentative quality\Nin your thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:52.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}犹如你的头脑被一大堆\N棋盘之外的杂事{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as if your mind were occupied\Nwith issues
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:54.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}所占领了\N就在你眼前.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,other than those on the board\Nbefore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:57.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}如此先入为主的成见\N不但会削弱一个人的决断力,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such preoccupation\Nnot only weakens one's resolve,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:00.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}还有远见.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but one's foresight as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:02.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}这是任何竞赛中的致命弱点,\N你必须同意这点,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A deadly failing in any match,\Nyou must agree,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.53,0:02:07.93,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}而且在这场特别的争夺战中,\N损失会是相当惨重的灾难,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in this particular contest,\Nquite disastrous,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:11.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}尤其我们押上命做赌注,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as we play for grave stakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:15.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}诸如此类的事\N你不容置疑.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the likes of which\Nyou have no doubt surmised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:19.34,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}把你的行动印在明天的报纸上.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Print your move in tomorrow's paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}要不我就会替你印.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or l will make it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:26.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,简直逼人太甚. 库珀,\N我不会让你离开我视线之内的.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tears it. Cooper,\NI'm not Ietting you out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 如果云顿想要杀我,\N我早就死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, if Windom wanted to kiII me,\NI'd aIready be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:33.98,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:38.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 还是打电话给皮特吧.\N- 对.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Better get Pete on the horn.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:41.64,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,露西, 打电话给皮特·马爹利,\N叫他马上赶过来这里.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, caII Pete MarteII,\Nget him over here right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.08,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,然后打电话给报纸.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then caII the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:47.09,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,查一下明天个人信息栏的\N最迟截稿时间.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find out the Iatest possibIe deadIine\Nfor tomorrow's personaIs coIumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:51.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}报纸和皮特, 收到.\N我会按章办事.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper and Pete, got it.\Nl'll do it alphabetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:59.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她真美.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was beautifuI.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:05.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我视她的爱如生命, 哈里.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was the Iove of my Iife, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的, 露西.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:15.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的, 知道, 告诉哈里\N我马上就到, 好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, yeah, just teII Harry\NI'II be right there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.57,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,皮特.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,盐和胡椒粉.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SaIt and pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:44.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,马上来, 小松狮.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming right up, poodIe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:49.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩一起\N就知道使坏.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two bring out the worst\Nin each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:54.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦, 皮特真是个人才.\N- 一个宫廷小丑人才.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh, Pete's a prince of a man.\N- A court jester.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:01.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 我要出去溜达了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WeII, I've got to mosey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:16.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再见, 可爱的帕卡族.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, you sweet Packards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 凯萨琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:27.82,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳, 我一直冀望\N在你体内那股狂怒的暴风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catherine, I'd aIways have hoped\Nthat time and age wouId meIIow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,会随着时间推移有所收敛.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that tempest raging inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看着你们俩\N十足一对傻帽似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching you two act\NIike the Hardy Boys
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:36.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我气就不打哪一处来.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aIways brings on stormy weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:39.01,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,格斯伍的事怎样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening with Ghostwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我和投资人谈过了,\N会面都安排好了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I taIked to the investors,\Nthe meeting is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.58,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天就去巴黎.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Ieave for Paris tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 伙伴回来了.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:49.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的乔西...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Josie...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我回家来了, 你想我么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, did you miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:03.62,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢, 她看来惊喜过度了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she Iooked surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:08.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 可怜的乔西.\N- 噢, 再怎么说, 她还是有魅力的.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Poor Josie.\N- Oh, she has her charms, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是, 可惜不长久了.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.09,0:05:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but not for Iong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.18,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,进来.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:32.32,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨, 哈里.\N- 省点气吧, 汉克.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi, Harry.\N- Save it, Hank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:36.54,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦? 心情不好?\N今早上撞邪啦 ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? Did you get up on\Nthe wrong side of the bed this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是违反了保释条例. 我泪流成河行了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I broke paroIe. Cry me a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:42.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你越过边境去加拿大.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You crossed the border into Canada.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你联系和安排毒贩\N在死狗庄进行交易.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You consorted with the drug deaIers\Nat Dead Dog Farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.39,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你还意图谋杀.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.29,0:05:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to kiII somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:51.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我准备起诉你\N企图谋杀里欧·强生.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm charging you with\Nthe attempted murder of Leo Johnson.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好了, 我想里欧被枪击那晚\N我正好在餐厅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WeII, I think it's safe to assume\Nthat I was at the diner
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:57.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这够保平安了吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the night that Leo was pIugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:00.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不信，欢迎你打电话去问--\N- 我有目击证人.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- But you're weIcome to caII--\N- I got a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:02.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看见你\N手里握着枪.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puts you at the scene\Nwith a gun in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:05.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 看来你这次\N是动真格了,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, you obviousIy seem serious\Nabout this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:10.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我打算提议来个交易.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm going to propose a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:12.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,一个可以将杀害安德鲁·帕卡\N的凶手逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about information\NIeading to the arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:17.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和定罪的\N信息交换怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and conviction\Nof Andrew Packard's murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:21.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,汉克·詹宁斯,\N污点证人.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hank Jennings,\Nwitness for the prosecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没门.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No deaIs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在告诉我\N你对企图谋杀里欧·强生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're teIIing me\Nyou're more interested
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这个案子，\N比杀安德鲁·帕卡的重犯,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the attempted murder\Nof Leo Johnson, feIon,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,更感兴趣是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than Andrew Packard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.38,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么对得住\N你的选民?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that gonna sit\Nwith your constituents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你是彻底没救了, 汉克.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're through, Hank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:38.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜, 哈里, 这不太好.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is, Harry, not too weII.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:41.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,特别是一旦他们发现了\N是谁暗算了安德鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EspeciaIIy once they find out\Nwho pushed the button on Andrew
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.92,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而你正好和她同床共枕.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that you're sIeeping with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:53.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕, 不好意思了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.24,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,带他出去.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:56.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,让他滚出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:03.21,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那个给我.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:11.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们从你身上\N取出来的子弹.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the buIIet we removed\Nfrom you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:14.10,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,而这一颗是从\N那个死人的头骨的挖出来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the one that was excavated\Nfrom the dead man's skuII.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:18.45,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,同一种子弹, 同一把枪, 同一个杀手.\N我们去抓她吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same buIIets, same gun, same kiIIer.\NLet's go get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.80,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 艾伯特, 稳住.\N- 库,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- AIbert, hoId your horses.\N- Coop,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我体谅你是极不情愿\N逮捕你老友记的女人,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate any reIuctance you have\Nfor busting your paI's oId Iady,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.86,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但这女人在你身上开了天窗\N由你躺在那儿去死.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the woman ventiIated you\Nand Ieft you for dead.
