Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.34,0:27:09.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我还记得1914年，在圣彼得堡,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.60,0:27:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember CapabIanca and Lasker,
