Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.69,0:27:55.99,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,艾伯特.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.95,0:27:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AIbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.21,0:27:59.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,干的好, 皮特.
