Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.33,0:28:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a match on the gun that\Nwhacked you with the powder residue
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.89,0:28:11.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,和乔西·帕卡手套上残留的一样.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.17,0:28:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on Josie Packard's gIoves.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.63,0:28:13.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,西雅图警方还\N找到了一个目击证人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.87,0:28:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SeattIe poIice have aIso\Ncome up with an eyewitness
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.85,0:28:16.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,确认就是乔西\N在发现尸体的地方下车的.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.11,0:28:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who positiveIy ID'd Josie Ieaving\Nthe car where they found the stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.07,0:28:18.60,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你还不打算逮捕这个婊子的话,
