Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.77,0:28:22.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我会把这当作是私人原因--\N- 艾伯特, 我能处理这事儿.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.01,0:28:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I wouId consider it a personaI--\N- AIbert, I can handIe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.97,0:28:36.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你刚已经处理了.
