Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.47,0:29:14.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,至终, 还有为能洞悉不同的智慧\N干一杯.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.70,0:29:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And endings, and the wisdom\Nto know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.43,0:29:19.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我对不起你, 安德鲁.
