Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.05,0:29:23.31,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,的确，我刚开始是恨你.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.34,0:29:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hated you at first, of course.
