Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.74,0:29:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PerfectIy normaI response.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.06,0:29:34.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但当我的愤怒渐渐平息,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.32,0:29:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As my anger diminished,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.51,0:29:38.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就回想起埃卡总有办法\N去说服别人做任何事.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.75,0:29:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recaIIed that Eckhardt has a way\Nof persuading peopIe to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.64,0:29:42.26,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 肯定是他的主意.\N- 对.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.89,0:29:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It was his idea, of course.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.87,0:29:45.17,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,是他让我干的.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.13,0:29:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.48,0:29:47.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他还说你从没爱过我.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.73,0:29:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he said you never Ioved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.88,0:29:50.79,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你娶我只是\N为了报复他.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.13,0:29:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just married me\Nto get back at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.01,0:29:52.67,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是真的,\N我真的非常爱你.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.27,0:29:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true,\NI did Iove you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.15,0:29:57.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了,\N那已经成为过去了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.41,0:29:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course,\Nthe same cannot be said for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.81,0:29:59.11,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别, 乔西,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.04,0:29:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PIease, Josie,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.29,0:30:01.81,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间不要再互相欺骗了.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.54,0:30:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iet there be no more Iies between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.12,0:30:06.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你做了.\N现在就得付出代价.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.35,0:30:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a job to do and you did it.\NNow you're paying the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.91,0:30:09.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,做任何事都是有后果的,\N我亲爱的.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.15,0:30:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every action has its consequence,\Nmy dear.
