Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.26,0:30:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poIice are cIosing in.\NIf you don't take action,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.35,0:30:16.40,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚就要在牢房里过夜了.
