Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.44,0:30:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't know I'm aIive.\NHe can get you out of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.39,0:30:40.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,去找他吧, 乔西.
