Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.42,0:31:24.04,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想去些\N我们从没去过的地方.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.69,0:31:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted us to go somepIace\Nwe've never been before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.47,0:31:26.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧.
