Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.37,0:32:40.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不用再为我担心了.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.64,0:32:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't worry about me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.64,0:32:42.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了那么多可怕的事\N我都
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.91,0:32:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been a part\Nof aII the horribIe things
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.64,0:32:44.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,身在其中.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.87,0:32:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that have happened.
