Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.42,0:39:39.69,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.69,0:39:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.86,0:39:42.87,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我会说，这么多年以来\N荷恩家族一直把自己管理的好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.12,0:39:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say that the Hornes have managed\Nto take care of themseIves just fine
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.04,0:39:44.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,远比你看起来的价值重要.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.29,0:39:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for more years than you can count.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.70,0:39:46.44,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管我们可能看起来\N很绝望的样子,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.93,0:39:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And desperate\Nthough we may seem,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.61,0:39:50.27,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在可见的将来\N这情形还会持续下去.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.86,0:39:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wiII probabIy continue to do so\Nin the foreseeabIe future.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.28,0:39:58.37,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.54,0:39:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.25,0:40:04.77,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前都去哪儿了?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.51,0:40:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been aII this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.99,0:40:07.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我指, 你不是忙着去拯救\N寡妇和孤儿，就是忙着要把我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.22,0:40:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, when you weren't busy\Nrescuing widows and orphans
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.13,0:40:11.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,世界改造的更美好，适宜居住\N但除此之外呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.35,0:40:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and making our worId\Na better pIace to Iive in.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.13,0:40:14.61,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在天涯海角.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.36,0:40:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The far corners of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.10,0:40:18.97,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你, 外面的世界很精彩,\N欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.36,0:40:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I teII you, it's gIorious out there,\NAudrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.63,0:40:25.50,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,但再什么说, 回到家的感觉还真好.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.90,0:40:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AII in aII, it's good to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.86,0:40:31.47,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我才18.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.11,0:40:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm onIy 1 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.78,0:40:35.78,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还有，鸡蛋的价格\N究竟怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.01,0:40:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what exactIy does that have to do\Nwith the price of eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.78,0:40:38.74,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.01,0:40:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.92,0:40:43.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝, 看时间都过了.\N我还有个预约呢.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.19,0:40:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God, Iook at the time.\NI have an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.97,0:40:46.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你能转告我父亲吗?\N- 当然了.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.26,0:40:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- CouId you teII my father?\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.32,0:40:48.28,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,好的. 再见.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.59,0:40:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.33,0:40:50.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,再见.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.59,0:40:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.94,0:40:57.12,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,回见, 杰克.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.20,0:40:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'II see you Iater, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.34,0:41:02.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,回见, 欧蕊.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.57,0:41:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'II see you, Audrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.33,0:41:21.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 雪莉? 嗨.\N- 嗨. 你好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.59,0:41:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- SheIIy? Hi.\N- Hi. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.29,0:41:23.90,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,还好. 你过得怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.53,0:41:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay. How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.08,0:41:27.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,就过日子呗. 来一口?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.33,0:41:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Iife. Drag?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.22,0:41:29.52,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你在等詹姆斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.47,0:41:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you waiting for James?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.70,0:41:31.00,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.93,0:41:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.13,0:41:33.96,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,其实，我是收到这些怪字条才来的.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.40,0:41:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ActuaIIy I got this reaIIy weird note.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.14,0:41:36.53,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,有人想我\N来这见他们.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.41,0:41:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody wants me\Nto meet them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.71,0:41:38.71,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,怪吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.97,0:41:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.06,0:41:42.15,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那就怪了, 看我有什么.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.31,0:41:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is strange, Iook what I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.94,0:41:45.33,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们好像都有事\N要一起谈了.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.18,0:41:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It Iooks Iike we aII have something\Nto taIk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.29,0:41:49.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,刚好.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.55,0:41:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.04,0:41:54.43,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}看那山峰高耸入云,\N犹如波涛延绵不断{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.29,0:41:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See the mountains kiss high heaven,\NAnd the waves clasp one another
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.61,0:41:58.70,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}没有一朵姐妹花会被宽恕\N如果它鄙视它的兄弟{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.86,0:41:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No sister-flower would be forgiven\Nlf it disdain'd its brother
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.88,0:42:03.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}阳光紧扣着大地,\N月光则亲吻着大海--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.16,0:42:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the sunlight clasps the earth,\NAnd the moonbeams kiss the sea--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.23,0:42:07.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}如果汝不吻我,\N这世间一切的甜蜜之事价值何在呢?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.50,0:42:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this sweet work worth,\Nlf thou kiss not me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.72,0:42:11.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我只能说.\N- 这太奇怪了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.97,0:42:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- This is weird.\N- I'II say.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.63,0:42:34.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是库珀. 是的, 凯萨琳.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.90,0:42:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooper here. Yes, Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.76,0:42:37.94,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,不, 不, 我刚回来不久.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.00,0:42:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I was just on my way over.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.46,0:42:40.16,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她在这儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.74,0:42:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.95,0:42:43.30,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,在托马斯·埃卡的房间.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.21,0:42:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thomas Eckhardt's suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.21,0:42:45.95,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.48,0:42:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.85,0:43:01.63,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,救命!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.12,0:43:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HeIp!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.98,0:43:03.51,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 救命啊.\N- 我爱你.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.23,0:43:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- PIease heIp.\N- I Iove you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.68,0:43:06.07,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别!\N- 乔西, 别这样. 看在上帝的份上--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.93,0:43:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- No!\N- Josie, pIease. For God's sake--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.25,0:43:09.65,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我. 别摸我!\N别伤害我.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.50,0:43:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me. Don't touch me!\NDon't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.30,0:43:35.56,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我站住.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.56,0:43:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.31,0:43:46.14,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他想杀我.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.60,0:43:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to kiII me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.49,0:43:50.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你也打算这样形容我吗,\N乔西? 我也想杀你?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.74,0:43:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you'II say about me,\NJosie? That I tried to kiII you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.02,0:43:53.02,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,那乔纳森呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.28,0:43:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.20,0:43:54.85,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,难道他也想杀你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.44,0:43:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he try to kiII you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.03,0:43:58.29,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,他要抓我回去.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.28,0:43:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was taking me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.82,0:44:00.73,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要开枪打我, 乔西?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.05,0:44:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you shoot me, Josie?
