Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.00,0:44:06.35,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道会有这么一天的.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.26,0:44:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this day was going to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.52,0:44:09.48,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要坐牢. 我不可以.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.76,0:44:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to jaiI. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.88,0:44:13.36,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,把枪放下, 乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.13,0:44:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it down, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.32,0:44:18.41,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哈里.\N- 把枪放下!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.57,0:44:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Harry.\N- Put it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.63,0:44:21.59,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哈里, 原谅我吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.90,0:44:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harry, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.77,0:44:24.25,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没想过要伤害你的.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.01,0:44:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never meant to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.58,0:44:40.84,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西. 乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.86,0:44:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie. Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.54,0:44:42.76,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.79,0:44:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.55,0:44:50.03,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,她死了.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.80,0:44:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.56,0:44:54.91,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,乔西.
