Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.56,0:45:47.13,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.79,0:45:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.62,0:45:59.06,Blue,,0000,0000,0000,,哦, 乔西.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.90,0:45:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Josie.
